867
00:57:40.581 --> 00:57:41.665
Naiintindihan mo

868
00:57:42.249 --> 00:57:43.417
anong ibig kong sabihin?

869
00:57:46.086 --> 00:57:49.631
Ang Senior Presidential Economic Advisor
sasamahan tayo sa lalong madaling panahon

870
00:57:50.132 --> 00:57:52.050
para sa draft dodging charges din.

871
00:57:59.975 --> 00:58:01.685
Magsaya ka, at makauwi ng ligtas.

872
00:58:02.561 --> 00:58:03.687
Tratuhin mo siya ng mabuti.

873
00:58:04.354 --> 00:58:05.689
Huwag palampasin ang isang detalye.

874
00:58:05.772 --> 00:58:06.857
Oo, sir.

875
00:58:09.526 --> 00:58:10.527
Mr. Kim

876
00:58:11.445 --> 00:58:14.907
